{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/animate-elements-at-variable-rates","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Animirajte elemente razlicitim brzinama","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Postoje razliciti nacini za promenu brzine animacije povezanih elemenata. Do sada se to postizalo koriscenjem <code>animation-iteration-count</code> svojstva i podesavanjem <code>@keyframes</code> pravila.</p>\n<p>Kao demonstracija, animacija sa desne strane ima dve zvezde koje se smanjuju i postaju providnije na 20% u <code>@keyframes</code> pravilu, sto daje efekat treperenja. Mozete izmeniti <code>@keyframes</code> pravilo za jednu od njih kako bi zvezde treperile razlicitim ritmom.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d78a8367417b2b2512ae5","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Promenite brzinu animacije elementa sa klasom <code>star-1</code> tako sto cete izmeniti njegovo <code>@keyframes</code> pravilo na 50%.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cZ89WA4","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301040,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/animate-elements-at-variable-rates"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  .stars {\n    background-color: white;\n    height: 30px;\n    width: 30px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    animation-iteration-count: infinite;\n  }\n\n  .star-1 {\n    margin-top: 15%;\n    margin-left: 60%;\n    animation-name: twinkle-1;\n    animation-duration: 1s;\n  }\n\n  .star-2 {\n    margin-top: 25%;\n    margin-left: 25%;\n    animation-name: twinkle-2;\n    animation-duration: 1s;\n  }\n\n  @keyframes twin